gen.antlr.sql.exprs

Class SearchExprsBaseListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • gen.antlr.sql.exprs.SearchExprsBaseListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SearchExprsListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener

    public class SearchExprsBaseListener
extends Object
implements SearchExprsListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of SearchExprsListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
